# ORIG TITLE    Champion’s League draw: Barcelona to play Paris . 
# ORIG CONTENT  The Champion’s League Quarter Finals have been drawn in Nyon, Switzerland with favorites Barcelona facing Paris Saint-Germain, perhaps the star draw of the bunch. Real Madrid will play Galatasaray. Last year’s finalists Bayern Munich will take on Juventus. And Malaga will play Borussia Dortmund. All the UK’s teams have already been knocked out of the league. Ties will take place on 2-3 April and 9-10 April. 
